## Thread Safety

```java
// DANGEROUS: SimpleDateFormat is not thread-safe
static SimpleDateFormat fmt = new SimpleDateFormat("yyyy-MM-dd");

// Multiple threads calling fmt.parse() = corrupted results

// DANGEROUS: HashMap not thread-safe
