## XML Processing (XXE)

```java
// DANGEROUS: Default XML parsers allow XXE
DocumentBuilderFactory factory = DocumentBuilderFactory.newInstance();
// Default allows: <!DOCTYPE foo [<!ENTITY xxe SYSTEM "file:///etc/passwd">]>

